EFN
'''EFN''' stands for "Evil Friends Network." It is a network or [[clique]] of friends in [[Atlanta]], GA. It has various rotating memberships and is characterized by very glamourous girls and lots of cute gay boys, particularly those of the [[goth]] variety. Permanent fixtures include [[girlvinyl]], muffintop, [[onefiftytwo]], eurotrashprince, amyzon2313, meemeedarling, scargrrl and others.

